<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal nunnem Belam Chingpa'n,
 Van gam phaicham hing nuomah;
 Hinna tui luonna mun ah ei pui ina,
 Chawlhdamna In nuom taka;
 Van hinna tui dawn dingin,
 A hehpihna thu leh sapna chuh gingun.

[V2]
 Kumsawt hinna tui dam dii-diei,
 Mi thiengte laituol lenna;
 Lal nunnem Belam Chingpa-
 Vanga suklat kipakum!
 Salem tuolnuom kumsawt hin kiemlo.

[V3]
 2. Lungkham, lungzinna beita,
 Thihna, lusun na umlo;
 Hinna thingnuoi dailim nuom takmai achun,
 Hinna khawvak zam vel ah;
 Lal nunnempa chawian in,
 Van go thil gihawih tawh laituol leng dingin.

[V4]
 3. Salem tuol nuoma lengte'n,
 Nun khuonuom lambang pakin;
 Lal nunnem leh zaidam chuh a chawian ui,
 Minlun Lalmang vangkhuo chuh;
 Sanggah nin-in nuom tan tin,
 Pak bang lunin la'n bangin hei tan au ie.</lyrics>
<title>IN THE HEAVENLY PASTURES FAIR</title>
<hymn_number>294</hymn_number>
</song>